      • resolvePermissions

        public Set<Permission> resolvePermissions(Group group)
        Description copied from interface: GroupPermissionResolver
        Returns a set of Permissions assigned to a particular Stormpath Group.

        Spring Security will check these permissions to determine whether or not a Authentication associated with the Group is permitted to do something.

        Specified by:
        resolvePermissions in interface GroupPermissionResolver
        Parameters:
        group - the Stormpath Group to inspect to return its assigned Permissions.
        Returns:
        a set of Permissions assigned to the group, to be used by Spring Security for runtime permission checks.
        See Also:
        AccountPermissionResolver
